title: Level 4 on EUW forum
body:
Hello here, I'm level 4 on EUW forum and can't post anywhere on it. Can anyone fix that for me :3 ?
Thanks by advance ^^.
Wonder why I'm on NA forum ? Read other lines above x').

replies.body: Sometimes an account needs to sync up to the boards before posting.  I see that you've synced now, so you shouldn't have anymore issues.  Let me know if you run into problems!
